          q_en: "How did you prioritize the 2,847 transactions during reconciliation? Were there criteria to determine which were most urgent?",
          a_en: "Yes, I created a scoring system based on 4 factors: 1) Transaction value (>$1M = highest priority), 2) Client type (HNWI clients = priority 1), 3) Age (>90 days = urgent), and 4) Regulatory risk (FATCA reportable = critical). This allowed us to tackle highest business impact transactions first. For example, transactions affecting top 50 HNWI clients were resolved in first 5 days, minimizing reputational risk."
