          q_en: "After implementing automatic scripts, was there any continuous monitoring or process refinement to avoid future backlogs?",
          a_en: "Absolutely. I implemented 3-layer monitoring: 1) Daily automated reports flagging any unreconciled transactions >24h old, 2) Weekly dashboard showing reconciliation metrics and trends, and 3) Monthly deep-dive analysis looking for new patterns. Also created 'Reconciliation Health Check' that runs every Friday, alerting if any anomalies are detected. This monitoring framework was adopted by Bradesco and prevented future backlogs."
